[Category "Bidding Conventions"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "bidding_conventions/jacoby_2nt_splinters"]
[Student "S"]
{Although you could show your singleton \C now it is usually more informative to show a second 5-card suit. So you say 4\D. Partner bids 4\H.  

Partner signed off, showing a minimum, so you have nothing further to say.}

